69 20-1-52.
70 The Georgia Student Finance Commission, in consultation with the University System of
71 Georgia and the Technical College System of Georgia, shall promulgate rules and
72 regulations necessary to carry out the provisions of this article. Such rules and regulations
73 shall provide for relief from sanctions previously imposed under this article against a
74 person whose conviction is subsequently overturned on appeal or through collateral relief."
75 SECTION 2.
76 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
